data.description: Magnificent 2019 custom built, Ranch Style Home, featuring vaulted ceilings in the primary bedroom, living room, and dining area. The primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet, double sinks, and a custom tile shower. Partial finished basement with room to grow.  Stainless steel appliances complement the alder graphite cabinets adorned with crown molding, and granite countertops throughout. A stunning stone fireplace with a mantle graces the living room, while tile floors enhance all bathrooms and the laundry room. Enjoy the front and back covered patios surrounded by a fully landscaped yard with sprinkler systems. Backs to open space. Neighborhood park is blocks away.  Don't let this opportunity pass you by.
